# Barbershop App (React Native)

A two-sided mobile app where **clients book appointments** and **barbers manage their schedule**.
Built as a portfolio project focused on UI/UX, component design, and realistic booking flows.

## Key features

### Client
- Browse barbers and specialties (card grid)
- Barber details with portfolio access and booking entry point
- Appointment selector with availability (partially/fully booked days)
- Profile with upcoming/past appointments and cancellation

### Barber
- Dashboard with “next appointment” and status chips (Booked / Completed / No-show / Canceled)
- View appointment details + update status
- All appointments grouped by date with status counters
- Profile management (prices, profile details, portfolio)

## Tech stack
- JavaScript
- React Native (Expo)
- NativeWind (Tailwind-style utility classes)
- React Navigation
- React Native Reanimated
- Local mock data + dev seeding for demo appointments

## Media
Screenshots: `./screenshots`  
Screen recordings (MP4): `./screenRecordings`

## Demo data & assets disclaimer
All names, phone numbers, and appointment data in this project are **fictional** and used for demo/testing purposes only.  
All profile and portfolio images shown in the app and in the screenshots are **AI-generated** and do not depict real people.
